title: FIRE_ACE_C130_CFD
summary: Aerosol data obtained by Colorado State University during May 1998 on the NCAR C-130 research flights as part of the First ISCCP Regional Experiment (FIRE3) Arctic Cloud Experiment (ACE). The data are in ASCII format. The primary measurements were of ice nuclei and condensation nuclei.
